{
  "stem": "24171.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, the whole camp was very kind of-- this is like a working place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "All right, we didn't have-- we had better food than all over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had like, twice a week, like a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was almost like a pudding, with macaroni in it, and it was sweet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was really good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, cabbage, cabbage.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first couple of weeks we got-- kind of-- I got kind of better acquainted, with the working place, there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I volunteered, whatever it was, something just to get a little bit more soup-- save for them, for my nieces, and then I had-- if I ate, already, in the kitchen a little bit more, then I could save my portion, already, for them.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- but in the beginning, as long as you got close-- not just me, in any camp-- if you got close to the trash, you were lucky, because you ate whatever you found, the pieces.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remembered over there, for-- from the cabbage, the pieces of leaves in the garbage.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we went and wiped [? it out, ?] [? the scent. ?] And we ate, till they assigned us to work, you know, the couple of days.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then, when we got assigned to there, and when they were night shift, and I used to go and help out in the kitchen, because I was finished with my work in the barracks-- to wash the floor and to see should be clean.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Every barrack had two other girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was with my cousin, Dora.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were those military, big things, what they cooked the potatoes in, in the-- in the peel-- called them the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they called me in, to pick out from the-- you know, because they were late.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
